welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Webster, a charming city known for its historic Main Street and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our beautiful city has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Greater Rochester International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Greater Rochester International Airport serves domestic flights operated by Delta and United airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Greater Rochester International Airport serves domestic flights operated by American and JetBlue airlines.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
